data.description: Ranch-style home with four bedrooms three full baths plus a two-car attached garage with a fully finished basement in prestigious Reunion! The bright eat-in kitchen has a Gas cooktop, walk-in pantry, large island with under-mount sink, upgraded cabinets with 42-inch uppers with crown molding, gourmet oven & and stainless-steel appliances! Home features: formal dining room, solar panels, whole house fan, stamped colored concrete patio, abuts greenbelt, fully fenced rear yard, and mountain views!! Super convenient for commuters! Located within 20 minutes of DIA and walking distance of all the amazing amenities available at the Reunion Recreation Center! Plus, Reunion pool, Reunion Park, Second Creek open space, South Lawn Park, Schools, and more!
